OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHundreds of post offices to
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstop selling lottery       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ftickets                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A fifth of post offices in the UK will 
OL,6, stop selling lottery tickets and       
OL,7, scratchcards, its operator has said.   
OL,9,FLast year, the Post Office ended its   
OL,10,Fgroup contract with the National       
OL,11,FLottery, giving branches a choice on   
OL,12,Fwhether to stock the products.         
OL,14,FAllwyn, which took over running the    
OL,15,Flottery days ago, said reasons ranged  
OL,16,Ffrom religious beliefs to low sales.   
OL,18,FBut one postmaster said he would have  
OL,19,F"lost a significant amount of money" if
OL,20,Fhe continued to sell them.             
